		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you're trying for the warbly chord effect, it's called arpeggio. Try setting arpeggio X to 4 (major third above root) and arpeggio Z to 7 (perfect fifth above root).
<br />
<br />You won't be able to reproduce the sound exactly because it's a C=64 SID tune, and the SID has a few filters that the NES doesn't.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


